{"tid":979173,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打知我部電腦咩事？","createTime":"2019-01-12T13:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T12:21:33.000Z","uid":96145,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31e7f5781d1ad45cb253c2d5899da4529174f9d0","tid":979173,"uid":96145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"前排部電部用用下突然freeze左 咁咪boot下機<br />\n再用用下又突然好似斷電咁熄機<br />\n之後依兩個情況就會randomly咁出現<br />\n有時用一陣就會突然熄機 有時用成日都冇事<br />\n最近依幾日情況開始嚴重d 成日都突然斷電式熄機 咪諗住似係火牛有事<br />\n今日走去買左隻牛 返屋企一插 開到機 跟住就run下d benchmark software<br />\n都冇咩問題 點知用用下又直接熄機 之後就每次開機都係未去Windows就熄機（4~6秒）有時又會自己開熄開熄開.....<br />\n試過蚊插所有野 都試過2條ram 分別插4個ram slot 8次都係開幾秒就熄機<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecd63daa0c5269ae65d6c3479272a9682261c91","tid":979173,"uid":160794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"3ded0694361ed7b53e4e808e56b39b585a116f5f","tid":979173,"uid":96145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"hardware:<br />\ni7 6700<br />\nasus gtx 1070<br />\nantec neoeco gold 550w<br />\n2 x hyperX 8gb ddr4<br />\nmb: gigabyte b150m-d3h"},{"pid":"0ba1209eee8e49c1928092acd2fb0a80ef2e3399","tid":979173,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hardware:<br />\ni7 6700<br />\nasus gtx 1070<br />\nantec neoeco gold 550w<br />\n2 x hyperX 8gb ddr4<br />\nmb: <strong>gigabyte b150m-d3h</strong></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4724a34f575d3a923415aa8cdf609d022e89b2","tid":979173,"uid":51592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ded0694361ed7b53e4e808e56b39b585a116f5f","tid":979173,"uid":96145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c